.TH "snd_hwparams_to_dma_slave_config" 9 "snd_hwparams_to_dma_slave_config" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hwparams_to_dma_slave_config \- Convert hw_params to dma_slave_config
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_hwparams_to_dma_slave_config
.BI "(const struct snd_pcm_substream *substream "  ","
.BI "const struct snd_pcm_hw_params *params "  ","
.BI "struct dma_slave_config *slave_config "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "substream" 12
PCM substream
.IP "params" 12
hw_params
.IP "slave_config" 12
DMA slave config
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function can be used to initialize a dma_slave_config from a substream
and hw_params in a dmaengine based PCM driver implementation.
